ROCKET_BASE_URL=https://sandbox.rocket.com.bd
ROCKET_CALLBACK_URL=http://localhost:3000/payment/callback

# ===========================================
# Development Notes
# ===========================================
# 1. The system automatically detects dummy credentials and enables mock mode
# 2. In mock mode, all payments will be simulated successfully
# 3. For production, replace all dummy values with real credentials
# 4. Set SANDBOX=false for production environments
# 5. Update callback URLs to your production domain

# ===========================================
# Testing with Mock Mode
# ===========================================
# With dummy credentials, the system will:
# - Generate mock payment IDs and transaction IDs
# - Simulate successful payments
# - Allow testing of the complete payment flow
# - Log all payment activities for debugging

# ===========================================
# Production Setup Checklist
# ===========================================
# [ ] Replace all dummy credentials with real ones
# [ ] Set SANDBOX=false for all gateways
# [ ] Update callback URLs to production domain
# [ ] Test with small amounts first
# [ ] Set up proper webhook endpoints
# [ ] Configure proper error handling
# [ ] Set up monitoring and logging
